caption.p: Cytotoxic effect and LC-ESI-QTOF-MS/MS analysis of compounds from sub-fraction no. 7.7. ( A) Cell viability of MDA-MB-231 cells after treatment with each eluted compound for 24 h. ( B) LC-ESI-QTOF-MS/MS chromatogram and the identified compounds (C1–C10). One-way ANOVA test was performed with multiple comparison corrections (Dunnett test). Data represent the mean ± SEM of three independent experiments. (* p < 0.05, ** p < 0.01, *** p < 0.001).
